The '''Minister of War''' was the civilian manager of war related subjects on [[Naboo/Legends|Naboo]]. The position had a seat on the [[Naboo Royal Advisory Council/Legends|Royal Advisory Council]], but was dissolved during the [[Great Time of Peace/Legends|Great Time of Peace]].

